    content: `
      <div class="w-detail"><section nodeleaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px 0px 24px; padding:0px; outline:0px; max-width:100%; box-sizing:border-box !important; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:17px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:0.544px; orphans:2; text-transform:none; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; white-space:normal; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial; text-align:center">&nbsp;</section>

<p data-pm-slice="0 0 []" style="text-align:center; text-indent:2em"><img alt="" height="415" src="/upload/59125669.png" width="553" /></p>

<section style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; background:#ffffff"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">8月14日，聚焦&ldquo;一带一路&rdquo;科技外交与国际合作的&ldquo;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><strong><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">古今交响&middot;一见钟秦</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">&rdquo;驻华外交官科技创新合作（西安）分享会在西安隆重举行。本次活动由陕西省人民政府新闻办公室、中央广播电视总台国际</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">在线联合主办，由</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><strong style="background:#ffffff; color:#404040; font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0pt; text-transform:none"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">陕西长安先导产业创新中心有限公司（以下简称&ldquo;长安先导&rdquo;）承办</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">十余国驻华外交官与各界代表齐聚长安先导国际创新人才交流中心，以科技为纽带聚焦前沿技术展示与高端思想对话，共同开启跨境创新合作的探索之旅。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></section>

<p style="margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><strong style="background:#ffffff; color:#404040; font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0pt; text-transform:none"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">长安先导简介：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">&nbsp;作为陕西省级重点打造的产业</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>创新平台，长安先导<span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">聚焦未来科技，着眼未来产业和新兴产业技术突破，按照&ldquo;政府引导、企业运营、市场推动、项目管理&rdquo;的市场化可持续模式，在航空航天、生命科学、人工智能、物质科学等领域，联合高校院所、产业链企业等科创主体，建立共性技术研发、概念验证中心、中试基地等技术攻关平台，构建&ldquo;创新资源整合、创新需求挖掘、科创服务平台&rdquo;为一体的创新生态，实现&ldquo;资源与需求匹配能力与服务兼备&rdquo;，集聚一批创新人才，催生一批尖端技术，产生一批科技成果，形成与新质生产力更相适应的新型生</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">产关系，当好科技创新和产业创新深度融合的有力组织者和紧密合伙人。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt">&nbsp;</p>

<section nodeleaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px 0px 24px; padding:0px; outline:0px; max-width:100%; box-sizing:border-box !important; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:17px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:0.544px; orphans:2; text-transform:none; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; white-space:normal; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial; text-align:center">
<p style="text-align:left"><span style="margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">大会上，西安市委宣传部副部长、人民政府新闻办主任李敏等领导发表了重要讲话。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<section>
<p style="text-align:left"><span style="margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal">在&ldquo;一带一路&rdquo;科技外交创新合作沙龙环节，奥联首席科学家程朝辉博士受长安先导邀请参与演讲。奥联通过全资子公司西安奥联汇智信息安全技术有限公司入驻长安先导位于西安高新区软件新城的科技示范创新园区，双方已在密码创新技术领域开展了实质性合作。程朝辉博士作为该环节发言人之一，就中小企业数据安全出海议题作专题演讲，剖析企业出海的三大挑战：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:left">​</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" height="412" src="/upload/59125670.png" width="549" /></p>

<p style="text-align:left">​</p>
</section>
</section>

<p><span style="margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span leaf="" style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><strong>政策合规挑战</strong>：各国对数据安全的要求日益严格：欧盟</font>GDPR<font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px">对个人隐私数据实施严格保护，</font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">越南《网络安全法》强制要求数据本地化存储。这些差异化的政策要求，使合规成本成为中小企业出海的重要考量因素。</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><strong style="font-weight:bold"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">信任建立挑战：</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">数据安全不同于实物产品，其保护效果难以直观呈现。要获得国际用户认可，需要依靠两方面：一是通过长期稳定的安全服务记录证明可靠性；二是获取国际权威认证，如通用准则认证</span></span></span></span></font></span><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">CC</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">、美国</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:Calibri"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">FIPS</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">认证、</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:Calibri"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">ISO 27001</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">信息安全管理体系认证、支付卡数据安全</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:Calibri"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">PCI DSS</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">等。</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><strong style="font-weight:bold"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">技术适配挑战：</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">以中国和马来西亚为例：中国已广泛应用生物识别技术，但在马来西亚等国家，人脸识别系统需要解决头巾佩戴带来的识别问题。在加密技术领域，中国有</span></span></span></span></font></span><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">SM</span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">系列密码算法标准，马来西亚有国家可信密码算法列表</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:Calibri"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">MYSEAL</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">，在马来西亚销售的密码产品需要实现技术兼容。</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">面对严峻挑战，程朝辉博士强调</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">&ldquo;一带一路&rdquo;倡议蕴含巨大动能，并为中小企业提供系统性解决方案：</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><strong style="font-weight:bold"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">善用政策</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:宋体"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><strong style="font-weight:bold"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">支持</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><strong style="font-weight:bold"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">：</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">&nbsp;国家通过一系列政策工具和&quot;一带一路&quot;绿色通道等机制为企业提供帮助。例如，&quot;中国-东盟信息港&quot;等平台提供的跨境数据流动政策，能够有效降低企业合规门槛。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><strong style="font-weight:bold"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">构建信任桥梁：</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">&nbsp;一方面通过国际认证建立互信，另一方面推广中国经验。我国已建立较健全的网络和数据安全认证体系，包括对标CC的中国国家信息安全产品认证，以及类似于FIPS的商用密码产品认证等。经过认证的产品显著提升了我国数字系统的安全性。这些产品认证获得更多国家认可后，将有效降低认证成本，加快信任关系建立。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><strong style="font-weight:bold"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">推广中国技术标准：</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">&nbsp;我国在数据安全领域已形成一系列基础技术和标准。例如，在密码技术领域，我们建立了完整的密码算法体系、检测和应用标准。我国研制的SM2/3/4/9算法已纳入ISO/IEC标准。在标准制定过程中，我们通过算法全球征集、面向跨国企业同步征集意见、中英文版本同步发布等方式，不断提高国际参与度。中国技术正获得广泛认可，这将为企业出海提供强大动力。例如，MYSEAL 2.0已将SM技术纳入受信任的密码技术。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><strong style="font-weight:bold"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">创新引领未来：合规入场，创新立身</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">程朝辉博士总结道，数据安全不仅是技术问题，更是国际竞争的重要方面。</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">&ldquo;一带一路&rdquo;的政策协同、国际认证的权威背书、中国技术的创新突破，</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="font-family:宋体"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">中小企业在全球市场的竞争力将不断提升。</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">&ldquo;合规决定入场资格，创新决定市场地位&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;这一行业箴言，为程博士的发言画下有力注脚。</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">当晚的</span></span></span></span></font></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important">&ldquo;科技创新人才外交之夜&rdquo;，程博士亦与各方代表就国际人才交流与技术合作进行了广泛沟通</span></span></span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; margin-bottom:24px; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px; text-align:center"><span style="font-size:17px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="clear:both"><span style="min-height:1em"><span style="color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)"><span style="font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:400"><span style="letter-spacing:0.544px"><span style="orphans:2"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="widows:2"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="text-decoration-thickness:initial"><span style="text-decoration-style:initial"><span style="text-decoration-color:initial"><span style="font-size:12pt; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent"><span style="outline:0px"><span style="box-sizing:border-box !important"><span style="overflow-wrap:break-word !important"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><span style="color:#404040"><span style="letter-spacing:0pt"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; box-sizing:border-box !important; margin:0px; max-width:100%; outline:0px; overflow-wrap:break-word !important; padding:0px"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin:0px; max-width:100%; padding:0px"><span style="outline:0px"><span style